---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="線上預約｜YoYo 驗光師｜多焦點鏡片 蔡司鏡片 兒童近視控制 高度近視眼鏡｜能見度視覺中心 × 比泱驗光所 新莊板橋"
  description="預約 YoYo 驗光師：多焦點鏡片諮詢、蔡司鏡片個人化訂製、兒童近視控制評估、高度近視眼鏡配製。能見度視覺中心 × 比泱驗光所，新莊、板橋門市。"
>
  <section class="bg-brand-navy text-white py-20 px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">線上預約</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">選擇你方便的時段，YoYo 驗光師會在預約時間準時為你服務。</p>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">預約須知</h2>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 text-sm">
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold">✦</span>首次驗光建議預留 60–90 分鐘</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold">✦</span>攜帶目前配戴的眼鏡與舊處方箋（如有）</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold">✦</span>前一晚充足睡眠，有助於調節力放鬆測量</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold">✦</span>若需散瞳驗光，請安排不需自行開車的行程</li>
          <li class="flex gap-2"><span class="text-brand-gold">✦</span>預約更動請於 24 小時前透過 LINE OA 告知</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-brand-light rounded-2xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">門市資訊</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-gray-600">
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-brand-navy">新莊店</p>
            <p>能見度視覺中心 × 比泱驗光所</p>
            <p>新北市新莊區中正路</p>
            <p>週一～五 10:00–20:00 ｜週六日 10:00–18:00</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-brand-navy">板橋店</p>
            <p>能見度眼鏡 × 能見度驗光所</p>
            <p>新北市板橋區</p>
            <p>週一～五 10:00–20:00 ｜週六日 10:00–18:00</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Google Calendar 預約嵌入 -->
    <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <div class="bg-brand-navy text-white px-6 py-4">
        <h2 class="font-bold text-lg">選擇預約時段</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm">透過 Google 行事曆即時選擇可用時段</p>
      </div>
      <iframe
        src="https://calendar.google.com/calendar/appointments/schedules/AcZssZ2OA49BwsrHGj2hA6fJknNGMnGCr_u9k8kMXRvBrOtB8Y2BEPxFJBxDI8_vxu_x5-e-VFZQ2b3V?gv=true"
        style="border: 0; width: 100%; height: 600px;"
        frameborder="0"
        title="能見度視覺中心線上預約"
      ></iframe>
    </div>

    <!-- LINE OA 備用 -->
    <div class="mt-8 text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-500 mb-4">或透過 LINE OA 直接聯絡我們</p>
      <a href="https://line.me/ti/p/beyondvisualopt"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-[#06C755] text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-[#05a847] transition-colors">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M19.365 9.863c.349 0 .63.285.63.631 0 .345-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755c.349 0 .63.283.63.63 0 .344-.281.629-.63.629h-2.386c-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63h2.386c.346 0 .627.285.627.63 0 .349-.281.63-.63.63H17.61v1.125h1.755zm-3.855 3.016c0 .27-.174.51-.432.596-.064.021-.133.031-.199.031-.211 0-.391-.09-.51-.25l-2.443-3.317v2.94c0 .344-.279.629-.631.629-.346 0-.626-.285-.626-.629V8.108c0-.27.173-.51.43-.595.06-.023.136-.033.194-.033.195 0 .375.104.495.254l2.462 3.33V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.345 0 .63.285.63.63v4.771zm-5.741 0c0 .344-.282.629-.631.629-.345 0-.627-.285-.627-.629V8.108c0-.345.282-.63.63-.63.346 0 .628.285.628.63v4.771zm-2.466.629H4.917c-.345 0-.63-.285-.63-.629V8.108c0-.345.285-.63.63-.63.348 0 .63.285.63.63v4.141h1.756c.348 0 .629.283.629.63 0 .344-.281.629-.629.629M24 10.314C24 4.943 18.615.572 12 .572S0 4.943 0 10.314c0 4.811 4.27 8.842 10.035 9.608.391.082.923.258 1.058.59.12.301.079.766.038 1.08l-.164 1.02c-.045.301-.24 1.186 1.049.645 1.291-.539 6.916-4.078 9.436-6.975C23.176 14.393 24 12.458 24 10.314"/></svg>
        LINE OA 預約
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
